nodes.text: A human male served as a coastal defender stormtrooper squad leader in the Scarif Deployment of the Galactic Empire during the Battle of Scarif. The trooper led a squad of other coastal defender stormtroopers, who were able to pinpoint the infiltration point of the Rebel Alliance Rogue One team. The squad leader found Bodhi Rook and ordered him to identify himself, but was killed by other rebels while the rest of his squad was ambushed.
